,"fix":"add an expression before the operator","hint":"Binary operators like +, -, *, =, etc. require both a left and right operand.\n\nFor example:\n  ```ocaml\n  let x = 1 + 2   (* correct *)\n  let y = 1 +     (* missing right operand *)\n  let z = + 2     (* missing left operand *)\n  ```\n\nIf you want to create a partially applied operator function, use parentheses:\n  ```ocaml\n  let add_one = (+) 1\n  ```\n"},"span":{"start":1845,"end":1846}},{"kind":{"id":"E0008","name":"invalid-expression","expected":"expression","found":{"kind":")","text":")"},"hint":"Expected a value, function call, or operator expression."},"span":{"start":1848,"end":1850}},{"kind":{"id":"E0020","name":"missing-binary-operand","expected":"left operand for %","found":{"kind":"%","text":"%"},"fix":"add an expression before the operator","hint":"Binary operators like +, -, *, =, etc. require both a left and right operand.\n\nFor example:\n  ```ocaml\n  let x = 1 + 2   (* correct *)\n  let y = 1 +     (* missing right operand *)\n  let z = + 2     (* missing left operand *)\n  ```\n\nIf you want to create a partially applied operator function, use parentheses:\n  ```ocaml\n  let add_one = (+) 1\n  ```\n"},"span":{"start":1852,"end":1853}},{"kind":{"id":"E0008","name":"invalid-expression","expected":"expression","found":{"kind":"unknown character '\\'","text":"\\"},"hint":"Expected a value, function call, or operator expression."},"span":{"start":1966,"end":1967}},{"kind":{"id":"E0008","name":"invalid-expression","expected":"expression","found":{"kind":"#","text":"#"},"hint":"Expected a value, function call, or operator expression."},"span":{"start":1966,"end":1966}},{"kind":{"id":"E0008","name":"invalid-expression","expected":"expression","found":{"kind":"#","text":"#"},"hint":"Expected a value, function call, or operator expression."},"span":{"start":1967,"end":1970}},{"kind":{"id":"E0007","name":"invalid-pattern","expected":"identifier or pattern","found":{"kind":"%","text":"%"},"fix":"ad